title: Amtlib.framework for Creative Cloud 2014
description:
amtlib.framework file for all CC 2014 products. 

1.Install any program from Creative Cloud, start the trial, close all Adobe programs, turn off internet.

2. Start disable_activation_osx file (included in this torrent), choose 1 (yes) in the terminal

3. Then go to you installed Adobe sowftware (Photoshop for example) in Applications /Adobe Photoshop CC 2014, in this folder right click on Adobe Photoshop CC 2014 program icon, choose show package contents, then choose Contents folder, and inside it open Frameworks folder

4. Drag amtlib.framework from this torrent to your Framework folder and REPLACE the file

5. That is all, you can even update your Adobe software via Creative Cloud application!
